Interface EgoCharacteristicsDistribution

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CliqueEgoDistribution, ToyEgoDistribution
    public interface EgoCharacteristicsDistribution

    Functional interface that create an Ego and a collection of CliqueStubs for a Person.

    Look at chapter 5 of this dissertation for a description of those concepts.

    Look at CliqueEgoDistribution for an example implementation.
